          "note": "Applies a move and updates everything that must stay consistent: captured piece (incl. the off-square en-passant pawn), promotion, the rook that moves alongside a castling king, the en-passant target, castling rights (via an elegant per-square mask), the 50-move clock, side to move, and occupancy.",
          "note_comments": [],
